    "body": "need to add a ``is_offset`` to ``pandas/_libs/src/inference.pyx``, then you can use this in ``isscalar``. this would look very similar to ``pandas/_libs/src/util.pxd/is_period_object`` (you don't need to define it *also* in util.pxd though).\r\n\r\n``is_offset`` should also be imported / tested in ``pandas/core/dtypes/common.py``"
